description: FireFox Gold Corp. engages in the exploration and development of gold deposits in Finland. Its flagship properties include the Jeesio project covering approximately 142 square kilometers located in Lapland; and the Mustajarvi project covering 1.5 square kilometers situated in northern Finland. The company was formerly known as Silverstone Resources Corp. and changed its name to FireFox Gold Corp. in August 2017. FireFox Gold Corp. was incorporated in 2017 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
